Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又回到 這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 什 麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber小姐回國了 真的很突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長就不必在晚上出門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經 不會再遇到危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我陪著Saber冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是我讓Saber陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我可能會更常出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以後就算我回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要站在門口等我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須打倒的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在這座鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央公園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個影子似的東西 到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和臟硯的關係也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被臟硯使役著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該只是被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得去問問遠坂才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捏 我捏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你還活著呢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把名字 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥的名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是士郎啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等 讓你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是敵人嗎 伊莉雅斯菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我伊莉雅就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御主們只能在晚上戰鬥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來和士郎聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前一上來就給了我一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在說要聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 這不是一回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪士郎那麼弱 還非要跳出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是現在 我也能殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要殺沒了Saber的士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒鐘都不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等到現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你陪我說句話也沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那伊莉雅你現在住在森林的城堡裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉和莉茲也和我住在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是好不容易躲過了塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專程跑來見士郎你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好引以為傲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再問一句可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對衛宮切嗣這個名字有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個名字 沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 我也正想找衛宮談點事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要談話的話在學校裡談不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 去沏杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛那副表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什麼昵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們來開始作戰會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去準備晚飯才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼不早點說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遠坂讓我插不上話才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門開著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放了櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會殺掉衛宮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想給他點苦頭嘗嘗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來做Rider的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以考慮放了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是為了戰鬥才來這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不應該一個人來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 怎麼回事 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼簡單就倒下了可是很無聊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的忍耐力 已經為你帶來了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 不用再放水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣殺了他 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 把這傢伙幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠 遠阪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和衛宮締結了同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也只是一直在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你利用了櫻那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就已經是我的敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 櫻 櫻 櫻 櫻 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種傢伙怎麼樣都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了御主的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮 快趴下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣把他們都收拾乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間桐家的血統已經衰敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再會產生會使用魔術的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為是臟硯召喚了Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後轉讓給慎二使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 事實上並沒有這麼複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的間桐家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最適合當御主的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間桐家正統的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一代的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令咒的轉讓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用令咒命令了Rider聽從間桐慎二的指令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 慎二成為了Rider的御主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這期間 你失去了作為御主的許可權
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淪落為了普通的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看著哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為令咒是間桐家發明的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能夠使出這種花招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把支配權讓給我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還裝什麼乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令咒還剩下一劃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二 如果令咒用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 就算再造出一本偽臣之書 也馬上就會燒毀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用借來的令咒去控制Rider的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從最開始就不是御主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道這種破辦法是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我 杷他們都宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你沒有遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明說了不會殺了學長的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 別看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她還控制不好能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不小心讓她吸收了魔力的話 她就沒法恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走開 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的主子已經失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 她就會耗盡魔力 等於是在自毀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要吸收的魔力比消耗掉的魔力多就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖 主子易改 本性難移啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是為了做這些事 才召喚你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法服從這個命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 您的生命優先於一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧 石化魔眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:22:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.16,0:23:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.96,0:23:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間桐櫻的治療也剛好完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和Rider一起把你們帶到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺禮 櫻的狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且留住了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 你的魔術刻印怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了治療間桐櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.44,0:24:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已 全部用盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.65,0:24:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 此次治療的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當是活的魔術回路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.80,0:25:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被刻印蟲啃噬
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.13,0:25:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就會滲透到身體的各個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.01,0:25:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命榨取生命的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.68,0:25:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用粘液刺激皮膚 並浸潤它
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令快樂中樞高揚 從而使其崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此來滿足它們的饑餓感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.57,0:25:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.19,0:25:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被這些蟲豸浸淫的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.41,0:25:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論身體還是精神
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.66,0:25:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會遭到刻印蟲的侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.62,0:25:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它們破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.29,0:25:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而間桐櫻也
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.75,0:25:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.67,0:25:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得需要說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.01,0:25:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要刻印蟲還在體內
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:25:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為生命能量的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.34,0:26:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會被無止境地吸乾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,置之不顧的話 她會死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.85,0:26:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術不是成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.60,0:26:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非全部驅除
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.15,0:26:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是積攢了11年的份
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.44,0:26:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強行驅除的話 身體會先受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把刻印蟲完全驅除
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.62,0:26:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種難如登天的事 只有借助聖杯的力量才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.88,0:26:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.81,0:26:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為冬木的管理者 就由我來處置她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.65,0:26:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處置 你是說間桐櫻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.86,0:27:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不能控制自己的力量的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.24,0:27:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能放她活路的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.78,0:27:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子已經是 失控的御主了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她是自己的親妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.96,0:27:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.30,0:27:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂家本來就有兩個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是魔術師家族註定一脈相承
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.15,0:27:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我繼承了遠坂家的魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.77,0:27:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻則作為血脈業已斷絕的間桐
Comment: 0,0:27:39.86,0:27:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(瑪奇里, Makiri)家的後繼者
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.86,0:27:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是瑪奇里家的後繼者
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.86,0:27:41.70,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(910,1005)}Makiri
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.20,0:27:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被收作養女
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.53,0:27:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.45,0:27:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和櫻確實是親姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.66,0:27:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說從未以姐妹相稱過
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.63,0:27:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.34,0:27:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就更不能
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.47,0:28:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣放著她不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.68,0:28:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會發生同樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就會毫無差別地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.52,0:28:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把無辜的人們捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.03,0:28:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要殺掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我輸給櫻了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.82,0:29:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 這個給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.14,0:29:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我 第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從最重要的人手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下了珍貴的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要趕在遠坂之前找到她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.06,0:30:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了櫻以後
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.81,0:30:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.19,0:30:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.03,0:30:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上不是要戰鬥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.54,0:30:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正士郎已經不算是御主啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.96,0:30:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.58,0:30:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider的御主倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.92,0:30:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就剩下兩個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.05,0:30:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎雖然想救Rider的御主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.43,0:30:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在就是找不到她人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.86,0:31:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 都要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.90,0:31:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 你不生我的氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.07,0:31:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會生氣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.95,0:31:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是士郎的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.95,0:31:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.09,0:31:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上說的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.88,0:31:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣的事 其實我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.05,0:31:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我是為了贏得聖杯戰爭才誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.14,0:31:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是伊莉雅的目的一直都是殺死切嗣和士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是士郎說 想要保護自己重要的人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.40,0:31:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是 士郎的同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.82,0:31:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護自己喜歡的人是理所當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.49,0:31:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.82,0:32:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的已經完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.78,0:32:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.91,0:32:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.47,0:32:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.43,0:32:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.68,0:33:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的感冒還沒好透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.14,0:33:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的這個藥水
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.98,0:33:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是什麼毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是讓感官更加敏感的藥物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.20,0:33:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅如此 我就控制不了自已了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.16,0:33:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還傷害了學長
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒傷到
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是那種程度的話 我完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.71,0:33:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是間桐家的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.04,0:33:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我一直都瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.84,0:33:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 都沒跟櫻說自己成了禦主的事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.59,0:33:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去學長家裡也是因為我不敢忤逆爺爺罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.64,0:33:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用幫學長的忙當藉口 一直在欺騙著學長
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.11,0:33:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直 一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.44,0:33:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不配陪在學長的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.91,0:34:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這種事就到今天為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就當你是不認識的人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.46,0:34:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在走廊裡遇到也不去打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.67,0:34:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後也裝成是陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.42,0:34:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地一個人回到家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.55,0:34:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把迄今為止的事都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.43,0:34:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.18,0:34:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想自殺的時候把小刀抵在手腕上還可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是欺騙學長
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.11,0:34:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是停止這樣的生活 我都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.36,0:34:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍全是可怕的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.57,0:34:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經一步都動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.87,0:34:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不知道該怎麼辦才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.66,0:34:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想繼續守護和學長在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 對我來說明明只有那才是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.59,0:35:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命唯一的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.98,0:35:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保護的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.48,0:35:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最重視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.96,0:35:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想讓她不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.41,0:35:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使誰都不責怪櫻 櫻也拼命自責的話
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.12,0:35:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會伸手 將她拉出陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.13,0:35:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果其他人不原諒櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.02,0:35:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就代替櫻 原諒她自己
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.57,0:35:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.07,0:36:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.49,0:36:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.24,0:36:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又會像剛剛那樣暴走失控
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.58,0:36:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有一天會做出無法挽回的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.42,0:36:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的我 還能有什麼容身之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.60,0:36:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡 就是櫻的家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.27,0:36:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.53,0:36:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.95,0:36:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就有了第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.12,0:36:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.29,0:36:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後又一直被好多奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵犯了我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.04,0:37:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪裡還有資格讓學長保護
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.85,0:37:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.77,0:37:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算櫻自己想殺死自己
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.02,0:37:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會保護櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.48,0:37:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.57,0:37:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做櫻一個人的正義使者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊學長
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.08,0:37:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣肯定會讓學長受到傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.26,0:37:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明會讓你受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.10,0:37:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.96,0:38:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.71,0:38:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.42,0:38:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.07,0:38:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是在保護至今為止的信念的話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.04,0:38:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無妨 結局已能揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 若你選擇了不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.34,0:39:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎便沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.09,0:39:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終 可是會失去一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.61,0:39:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了吧 好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.16,0:39:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發燒了嗎 剛剛淋了這麼久的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.83,0:39:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.05,0:39:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力有一點點 不太夠
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.59,0:39:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我能幫你點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.76,0:39:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.48,0:40:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.77,0:40:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.23,0:40:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 給我一點血就好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.74,0:40:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.99,0:40:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.75,0:40:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.86,0:40:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.53,0:40:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.96,0:41:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.14,0:41:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.60,0:41:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.89,0:41:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能沾汙了學長
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 幫我做一下出汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.88,0:41:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菠菜要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.35,0:42:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就用芝麻拌一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.06,0:42:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 幫我拿個雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.18,0:42:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.19,0:42:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.66,0:42:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很久沒有這樣一起吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.95,0:42:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.46,0:42:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不先吃起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.75,0:42:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用這麼客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.92,0:42:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從者不需要像你們這樣攝取營養
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.97,0:42:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 Saber倒是吃得很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.64,0:42:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太習慣你們的吃法
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.86,0:42:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 這個簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.04,0:43:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於今後的行動方針
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓櫻獲勝 讓她使用聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.54,0:43:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得 櫻還是待在家裡不要出去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.63,0:43:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接和臟硯見面太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.93,0:43:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.26,0:43:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你打算如何打倒那個魔術師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.60,0:43:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得必須和其他御主聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.77,0:43:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有哪些御主可以合作昵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.99,0:43:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂的Archer 櫻的Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.07,0:43:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臟硯手下有Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.54,0:43:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就是伊莉雅的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.29,0:43:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.50,0:43:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.96,0:43:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.38,0:44:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻不要出家門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.14,0:44:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.52,0:44:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在後悔也來不及了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.99,0:44:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 要是前輩陷入危險 就把他帶回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.66,0:44:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.16,0:44:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得比起那位長者
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.79,0:44:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們更應該去提防那個神父
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.80,0:44:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 實際上我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.89,0:44:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你放心吧 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.64,0:44:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那個人 根本贏不了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.40,0:44:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.11,0:45:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前 輩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.47,0:46:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 不讓他出門就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.76,0:46:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 就再也不會碰到危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.60,0:46:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.38,0:46:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是艱辛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.52,0:47:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是讓我跟著它走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.74,0:47:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.17,0:47:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會掉在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.63,0:48:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的主人很像
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.97,0:48:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個懦弱的從者
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.34,0:48:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全感受不到要和我們一戰的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.10,0:48:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命就這麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.44,0:48:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.11,0:48:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的願望便是不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.36,0:48:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我這身體
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.11,0:48:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每時每刻都在腐爛著
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.95,0:48:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發著腐臭
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.37,0:48:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長年積累的智慧正在流失
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.37,0:48:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.71,0:48:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活生生地腐爛下去的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.25,0:48:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種小輩能明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.29,0:48:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上沒有不畏懼死亡的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.18,0:48:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能實現我的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.97,0:49:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我要把世界上所有人一個個殺掉都行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.03,0:49:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你徹底失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.74,0:49:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經徹底遺忘了你的目標了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.28,0:49:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪奇里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.24,0:49:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回想起我們的夙願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對奇跡的渴望來自於何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.75,0:49:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.13,0:49:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才以人類之身向非人境界前進的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.64,0:49:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區人偶 也能說出這番話
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.98,0:49:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是把祖先的言行也填裝進軀體裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.77,0:49:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒戲就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.49,0:49:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛因茲貝倫的聖杯 就由我間桐臟硯來收下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.44,0:50:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過去 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.17,0:50:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂 你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.13,0:51:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到 衛宮和我不謀而合了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.54,0:51:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.77,0:51:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快從那裡離開
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.56,0:51:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它拖下去的話就回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.50,0:52:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.21,0:52:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.04,0:52:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別白白把愛因茲貝倫的小姑娘放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.64,0:52:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.98,0:52:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.94,0:52:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.17,0:52:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.76,0:53:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.60,0:53:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的對手 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.49,0:53:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.52,0:54:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.91,0:54:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正統的英靈
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.45,0:54:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法抵禦它的咒層界的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.54,0:54:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你 已經和林中彷徨的怨靈沒什麼區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.11,0:54:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.82,0:54:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.91,0:54:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.91,0:54:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.04,0:55:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker！
Comment: 0,0:58:06.73,0:58:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（(誓約,Excalibur)）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.73,0:58:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H80&}（誓約）
