Comment: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（(勝利之劍,Morgan)）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H80&}（勝利之劍）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.07,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H80&\fs38\pos(960,1005)}Morgan
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.60,0:58:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.90,0:59:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經完成了我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.27,0:59:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下就交給閣下了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.90,0:59:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.32,0:59:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能彌補之前的狼狽了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.16,0:59:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.76,1:00:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.61,1:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.28,1:00:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.66,1:00:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.46,1:00:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.42,1:00:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不偷襲的話 連毛孩子都殺不掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.71,1:00:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.84,1:00:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.09,1:00:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還能到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.39,1:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道昵
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.93,1:00:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.68,1:00:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.60,1:00:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那個追上來了的話就完了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.03,1:01:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討論留在後面
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.53,1:01:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來 小子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.53,1:01:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已經牽起了伊莉雅的手
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.74,1:01:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼直到最後一刻為止都要保護好她
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.75,1:01:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.23,1:01:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.49,1:01:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還能動
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.03,1:01:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.24,1:01:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和其他英靈不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.12,1:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什麼能被稱為「英雄」的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.66,1:01:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是什麼正統的英靈
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.71,1:01:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也因此 能和些許污穢共存
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.00,1:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.08,1:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本身就是扭曲的英靈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.15,1:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.70,1:02:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經可以變回靈體了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.41,1:02:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊時間從這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.87,1:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.70,1:02:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.75,1:02:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.05,1:02:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.05,1:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.89,1:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點跑啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.89,1:02:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.28,1:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力正在聚集
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.78,1:03:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.45,1:03:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來 遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.59,1:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am the bone of my sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.63,1:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Steel is my body.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.56,1:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have created
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.14,1:03:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,over a thousand blades.
Comment: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(熾天覆七重圓環,Rho        Aias)
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熾天覆七重圓環
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.44,1:03:47.19,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(960,1005)}Rho        Aias
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.65,1:04:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.62,1:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.83,1:04:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.75,1:04:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.92,1:04:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.93,1:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要保重啊 遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.28,1:05:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.96,1:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼做的話你也會
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.17,1:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想都不用想
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.63,1:05:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不做的話兩個人都會死
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.22,1:05:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼做的話確保有一個人活下來
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.94,1:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.65,1:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.24,1:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包成這樣確實挺嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.08,1:06:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 只是受了點小傷而已
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.54,1:06:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然纏了一圈又一圈的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.00,1:06:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.67,1:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實不要緊啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.92,1:06:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 遠坂是我在那邊遇到的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.38,1:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她救了我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.89,1:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以暫時停戰了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.51,1:06:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 這位是伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.39,1:06:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 雖然很突然
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.27,1:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.36,1:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂 能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.15,1:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.32,1:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.91,1:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給人類移植從者的身體
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.66,1:06:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事也太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.95,1:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.21,1:06:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕一次 只要使用了這只手臂的話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.42,1:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer的魔術回路就會啟動
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.13,1:06:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 你的身體無法承受
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.13,1:06:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行使魔術帶來的負擔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.34,1:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會從內部開始崩壞
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.97,1:06:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這布是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.68,1:07:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是封印
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.48,1:07:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠阪 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.98,1:07:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 幹嘛 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就打算在打倒間桐臟硯之前要和你聯手的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.15,1:07:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 能在櫻身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.86,1:07:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是正合我意
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.12,1:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在為櫻著想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.17,1:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 說得不對
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.56,1:07:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是4年前吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.94,1:07:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直練習助跑跳高練到傍晚對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.95,1:08:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不可能成功
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.53,1:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還一直在跳 真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.66,1:08:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就那樣站著 傻傻地對著你這個笨蛋看了很久
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.21,1:08:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果覺得自己做不到的話
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.63,1:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很果斷地放棄的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.96,1:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從根本上就是個很冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.97,1:08:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 畢竟我也是個魔術師嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.93,1:08:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時正想著「我的人生就這樣繼續下去真的好嗎」
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.93,1:08:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這種時候 看到了和自己完全相反的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.77,1:08:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時還挺受刺激的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.62,1:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搶走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.54,1:08:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要連這份回憶都搶走啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.60,1:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.91,1:09:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這布揭開以後一看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.33,1:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經恢復原樣了也說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.56,1:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.98,1:09:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.53,1:10:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.58,1:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.33,1:10:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻的幸福 就是你活著 並陪伴在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.63,1:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經不期盼其他的任何事了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.59,1:10:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望她能一直活著
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.97,1:10:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.22,1:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡她啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.19,1:10:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.65,1:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是櫻的夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.90,1:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論未來發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.49,1:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一直是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.33,1:10:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.33,1:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.17,1:11:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是魔力不足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.38,1:11:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來等著吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.39,1:11:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美工刀在哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.42,1:11:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.13,1:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.85,1:11:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會保護我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.64,1:11:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.40,1:12:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我更想讓櫻待在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.19,1:12:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.65,1:12:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分別這種事 想都不敢想
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.16,1:12:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想讓我作為家人待在身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.08,1:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.25,1:12:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為女孩子 待在身邊呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.30,1:12:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.51,1:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.56,1:12:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.14,1:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請和我做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.40,1:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.95,1:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.74,1:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很髒嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.87,1:12:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.08,1:13:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我僅僅是進了學長的房間
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.33,1:13:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已經這樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.63,1:13:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我自己動手自慰
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.84,1:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也完全壓抑不住這種欲望
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.47,1:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦子裡已經無法思考學長以外的事了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.51,1:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此骯髒的我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.69,1:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.36,1:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不骯髒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.94,1:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.95,1:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.69,1:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.56,1:14:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛姐姐把學長帶走了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.49,1:14:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅如此 我就害怕的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.01,1:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.55,1:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.10,1:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.57,1:14:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.37,1:15:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.25,1:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.76,1:15:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.68,1:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.02,1:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.31,1:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福正在成形的另一個聖杯
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.86,1:15:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正孕育著 被稱為「此世間全部之惡」的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.57,1:15:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由人類產生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.03,1:15:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人類又對其避之不及的某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.91,1:15:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善惡之所在
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.37,1:15:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是給出回答
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.46,1:15:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是生下能夠給出回答的東西的話
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.92,1:15:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.26,1:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案馬上就要揭曉了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.76,1:16:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果說這些問題是對於神的冒瀆
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.76,1:16:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我便在神面前 全心全意地
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.52,1:16:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我主問倒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.40,1:16:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始要承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.99,1:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少早飯就讓我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.58,1:16:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去幫遠阪學姐的忙了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.38,1:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.30,1:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.30,1:16:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你對遠阪
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.39,1:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.31,1:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我先把這邊的蔬菜洗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.27,1:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那就拜託
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.32,1:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 這麼叫很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.37,1:17:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.33,1:17:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並 並 並沒 沒有什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.97,1:17:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 那件事能在我房間裡做嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.60,1:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼事
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.85,1:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊 也是需要一兩件秘密兵器的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.23,1:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer的手臂裡
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.82,1:17:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是有著艾因茲貝倫的研究成果的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.44,1:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和遠坂說 一起看看有沒有辦法活用這個成果
Comment: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我對(基修亞•澤爾裡奇,寶石翁)留下的東西沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我對基修亞•澤爾裡奇留下的東西沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.87,1:17:50.91,RUBY,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(816,1005)}寶石翁
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.29,1:17:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得 魔法使留下的寶箱
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.67,1:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會很美麗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.05,1:18:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基修亞•澤爾
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.55,1:18:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.80,1:18:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.64,1:18:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.35,1:18:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.94,1:18:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都只是在遠處眺望著
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.11,1:18:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒想到真的會有
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.23,1:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能叫她「姐姐」的一天
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.53,1:18:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從到了間桐家之後
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.66,1:18:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有與遠坂見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.78,1:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.24,1:18:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是我還是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.16,1:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是互相知道
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.96,1:18:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是自己的姐妹這個事實
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.83,1:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相交流什麼的 是在極力避免的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.67,1:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.92,1:18:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果姐姐知道了我的魔術的話
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.64,1:18:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會討厭我的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.55,1:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被遠坂討厭
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.56,1:18:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.27,1:18:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間桐家的魔術
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.06,1:19:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從一開始 就只是為了從人身上奪取某些東西而使用的魔術
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.03,1:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一味地奪取
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.78,1:19:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個不會讓人喜歡的魔術
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.28,1:19:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 你討厭間桐家的魔術嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.29,1:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是非常嚴厲的教學方式
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.38,1:19:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但光論辛苦程度的話 是比不上學長的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.30,1:19:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是見過的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.97,1:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晚上 學長是多麼辛苦地訓練著
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.72,1:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經有很多次想阻止學長
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.94,1:19:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長的鍛煉是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.11,1:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是 自己刺穿自己的喉嚨一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.74,1:19:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是被他人強迫進行這種訓練
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.24,1:19:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是獨自一人固執地堅持著
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.25,1:20:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們之間 學長一定是最厲害的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.92,1:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因為魔術特性
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.30,1:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因為學長的內心純正
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.94,1:20:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從第一次遇見的時候 我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.40,1:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人一定 不會背叛任何事物
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.20,1:20:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮 是你 奪走的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.90,1:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 什麼反應都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.26,1:21:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.22,1:21:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雜草變黑了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.18,1:21:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 是那個黑影幹的 是受臟硯指使的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.56,1:21:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好說 我不認為他會留下這些證據
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.03,1:21:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 沒有味道
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.79,1:22:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真溫暖
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.04,1:22:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 還能感覺到溫度
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.80,1:22:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一刻能一直持續下去該多好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.09,1:23:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜靜的散步
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.85,1:23:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搖晃的腦袋空白一片
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.81,1:23:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標滿滿但心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.15,1:23:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咕嚕咕嚕的轉圈 go go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.77,1:23:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫斯庫斯的唱歌 go go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.49,1:23:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾枯的手腳像紙氣球 滾落在地
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.12,1:23:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到長大成人 才能輕飄飄地飛起來
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.96,1:23:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go Go!  Go Go!  Go Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.12,1:24:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎歧嘎吱 有人走了過來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.87,1:24:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只聽見 哈哈大笑聲
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.87,1:24:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有 感到過害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.52,1:24:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘰嘰喳喳 太吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.28,1:24:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子開始 咕咕叫
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.92,1:24:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠賣力的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.42,1:24:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那時候我說了讓你去死了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.94,1:25:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃閃發光 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.33,1:25:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緩刑期結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.04,1:25:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當這是我對你的慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.89,1:25:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.11,1:26:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到不只是影子 連身體都已經產生了變化
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.72,1:26:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想讓本王跪下
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.84,1:27:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.24,1:27:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到 已經到了到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.69,1:28:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.74,1:28:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.39,1:28:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.56,1:28:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上到客廳來
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.34,1:29:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.67,1:29:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著 我馬上拿治療道具來
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.63,1:29:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.60,1:29:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別發現 快停下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.28,1:29:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去想 「相似」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.75,1:29:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.76,1:29:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.80,1:29:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.64,1:30:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.64,1:30:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻的身體 只是看上去完好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.23,1:30:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上手腳的筋脈全都斷裂破碎了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.36,1:30:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 絕對已經死過一次了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.57,1:30:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不知道誰是兇手
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.37,1:30:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不只是身體上的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.41,1:30:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的大腦可能也被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.16,1:30:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須儘快打倒臟硯和那個影子才行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.63,1:30:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 我們要盡我們所能
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.09,1:30:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.43,1:30:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一臟硯和那個黑影沒有任何關係的話
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.14,1:30:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.83,1:31:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旱上好 自己的意識還在嗎 櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.12,1:31:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼龐大的靈魂 你是從哪裡吸收到的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.54,1:31:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明Assassin和Rider都還在
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.80,1:31:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已經飽和了 真讓人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.39,1:31:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 你知道接下來你會變成什麼樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.27,1:31:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.44,1:31:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死的 絕對 不會得救
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.08,1:31:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 好不容易能回來看看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.29,1:31:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 士郎 不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.34,1:31:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.72,1:32:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 士郎跑去哪了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.89,1:32:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明現在是小櫻最需要關照的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.27,1:32:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.28,1:32:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長說 會保護我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.12,1:32:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.29,1:32:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我犯的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.42,1:32:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長的夢想破碎了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.42,1:32:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.21,1:32:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 我是壞人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.26,1:32:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎是遇見壞人一定會斥責的人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.27,1:32:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻也想改掉自己壞的地方 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.78,1:32:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.19,1:33:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.20,1:33:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且 士郎的夢想是要做正義的夥伴不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.28,1:33:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想保護的人不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.25,1:33:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣的話 就不應該偏袒我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.58,1:33:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎的目標是切嗣先生的話
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.09,1:33:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有重要的人也是沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.30,1:33:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣先生也是個很偏心的人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.48,1:33:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個城市定居之後也是
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.40,1:33:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣先生也會一次又一次地跑去海外
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.61,1:33:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他的身體動不了為止 他一直都在這樣做
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.08,1:33:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有個無論如何都要見到的人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.63,1:34:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能見到重要的人 是非常痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.09,1:34:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是正義的夥伴也是如此
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.30,1:34:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 小櫻要好好陪在士郎的身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.45,1:34:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要背叛嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.17,1:34:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要背叛 曾經的自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.10,1:34:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.27,1:35:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要背叛的話 你會
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.57,1:35:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.79,1:35:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不會是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.22,1:35:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎 對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.27,1:35:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術師大人有話要對你說
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.75,1:36:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中到得早啊 叫衛宮的小子
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.00,1:36:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臟硯 我要說的話只有一句
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.84,1:36:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊把櫻解放了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.22,1:36:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放嗎 這麼說也行吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.69,1:36:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎 今天叫你過來 是有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.32,1:36:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓你把那個黑影給殺了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.49,1:36:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的同夥吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.03,1:36:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同夥嗎 你覺得那是能和人類交流的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.25,1:36:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚開始連安撫它都做不到了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.42,1:36:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 在那之前 得先告訴你那個黑影到底是什麼東西才行
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.68,1:36:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直說了吧 那是聖杯的內在
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.56,1:37:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從被稱為「聖杯」的門裡溢出的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.11,1:37:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是黑影的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.99,1:37:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影和 門
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.95,1:37:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛說要你把黑影殺掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.70,1:37:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那應該是非常困難的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.25,1:37:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 把門殺掉 是做得到的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.34,1:37:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和遠坂家的小姑娘想動手的話 會被發現
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.21,1:37:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂從者 也不過是飼料而已
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.18,1:37:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.35,1:37:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我種植下了聖杯的碎片
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.68,1:37:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我培養了十年的間桐家的聖杯 能把她殺掉的只有
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.40,1:37:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.07,1:37:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經察覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.20,1:37:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和櫻 很相似啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.50,1:38:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把存在於那裡的人偶
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.13,1:38:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借由心愛的男人之手將其終結而已
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.71,1:38:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也應該也是她的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.51,1:38:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.97,1:38:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦櫻自己的意識變成了空殼
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.01,1:38:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿在潛意識中的聖杯意識就會浮現
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.44,1:38:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前的災害就會重現吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.36,1:38:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想拯救櫻的話
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.11,1:38:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得忍耐到聖杯戰爭的期限結束
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.78,1:38:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從過去的例子來看還有4天吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.29,1:38:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.58,1:38:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得櫻能堅持到那個時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.92,1:38:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.13,1:38:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對能堅持到那時候
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.67,1:38:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其他人類可就不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.80,1:38:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為昨晚的暴食
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.34,1:39:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能現在肚子是挺飽的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.85,1:39:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 最快的話可能明天
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.27,1:39:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就會再次行動
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.94,1:39:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得需要多少天 它就會把這個城市的人吃光呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.24,1:39:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能明白
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.66,1:39:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了萬人除惡
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.91,1:39:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你繼承了衛宮切嗣的志向
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.66,1:39:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間桐櫻 才是你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.73,1:39:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.07,1:40:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.03,1:40:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 學長
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.06,1:41:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 這次聖杯戰爭結束後 有沒有什麼想做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.91,1:41:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 想不到有什麼要做的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.29,1:41:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得只要能和學長在一起 就夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.08,1:41:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我們一起去哪裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.84,1:41:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.63,1:41:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我想去 賞花
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.23,1:41:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就說好咯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.25,1:42:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用被冰凍結的心 做出溫暖的幻想
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.25,1:42:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待到何時冬日遠去 嶄新的春天來臨
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.17,1:42:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你我二人 一起去賞櫻花吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.45,1:42:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 等春天到來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.62,1:42:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.54,1:43:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫間桐櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.55,1:43:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從十分珍視的人手中得到如此重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.18,1:43:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想繼續守護和學長在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.81,1:43:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.97,1:43:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學 長
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.94,1:44:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要背叛自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.49,1:44:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當然了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.78,1:44:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你 學長
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.20,1:44:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從你那裡得到了很多東西
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.24,1:44:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.29,1:45:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能叫你姐姐 我真的是很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.75,1:45:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤村老師 謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.76,1:45:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我沒能遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.48,1:45:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider 謝謝你手下留情 沒有殺死學長
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.86,1:45:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.24,1:45:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後的令咒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.29,1:45:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.80,1:45:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去阻止爺爺
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.84,1:45:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可能已經來不及了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.76,1:45:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能再給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.39,1:46:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻 早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.56,1:46:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.88,1:46:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 你個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.38,1:46:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來得可真夠晚的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.31,1:46:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.10,1:46:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.65,1:46:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著這個試試
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.99,1:46:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是危險的玩意
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.92,1:47:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.51,1:47:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻你可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.01,1:47:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好哪天就能超過遠坂了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.48,1:47:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 哥
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.08,1:47:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自大了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.29,1:47:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是我的人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.13,1:47:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又一次搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.80,1:47:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會被如此殘暴地對待
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.09,1:48:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 還是和往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.68,1:48:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍忍耐一會兒就好
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.06,1:48:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.23,1:48:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐下去忍耐下去
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.40,1:48:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.90,1:48:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.82,1:48:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不願意
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.41,1:48:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經是學長的人了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.83,1:48:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.04,1:48:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來他把你調教得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.87,1:48:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.84,1:48:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.55,1:48:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼每次都會是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.43,1:48:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從很久以前就這樣想了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.26,1:48:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在恨著他
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.85,1:48:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我所處的世界周遭
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.77,1:48:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此地嫌棄我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.61,1:49:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 要告訴衛宮才行
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.61,1:49:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止 你多少次投入我的懷中
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.50,1:49:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多麼骯髒地和我做過
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.42,1:49:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種人 如果不存在多好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.70,1:49:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 哥
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.30,1:50:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.82,1:55:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H15&\fs130\pos(960,750)\fad(500,1500)}下  集  預  告
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.06,1:55:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.82,1:55:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成為只屬於櫻的正義的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.49,1:56:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 咬緊牙關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.39,up,NTP,0,0,0,,調查正在進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.06,up,NTP,0,0,0,,今早警方進入現場時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.31,up,NTP,0,0,0,,發現寺廟的建築物有一部分發生了崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.32,up,NTP,0,0,0,,現在由前方發回報道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.32,up,NTP,0,0,0,,位於東木市深山町円藏山中的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.86,up,NTP,0,0,0,,柳洞寺所發生的崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.54,up,NTP,0,0,0,,如大家所見 目前已經被封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.91,up,NTP,0,0,0,,無法看到內部的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.25,up,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的建築崩塌所涉及的建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:38.21,up,NTP,0,0,0,,這座柳洞寺的崩落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.68,up,NTP,0,0,0,,是由寺內原有的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:54.17,comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{/fs:35}出汁:從鰹魚乾及曬乾的海帶中提取製作而成的日式調味品
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.37,1:07:27.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 這是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.54,1:07:32.34,up,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我要是沒有成為御主的話
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.84,1:07:34.67,up,NTP,0,0,0,,也就不會認識遠坂了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.97,1:07:43.85,up,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎樣我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.22,1:07:47.48,up,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很早之前就知道你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.49,1:08:00.49,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時也在現場
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.75,1:21:26.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,下一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.29,1:21:32.09,up,NTP,0,0,0,,在東木市新都的中央公園發現了疑似被殺害的人的遺體
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.63,1:21:33.72,up,NTP,0,0,0,,被害者有四人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.30,1:21:38.10,up,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園的長椅上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.51,1:21:39.56,up,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了遺體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.19,1:28:48.36,up,NTP,0,0,0,,本日22點30分左右新都站周邊發生了大規模停電
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.15,1:28:54.41,up,NTP,0,0,0,,並且 警方接到了大量奇怪的報案
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.87,1:28:57.70,up,NTP,0,0,0,,據稱「身邊的人不見了」 「下落不明」 「突然消失了」
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.82,1:29:39.66,up,NTP,0,0,0,,目前已知的被害人已超過60人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.87,1:29:45.29,up,NTP,0,0,0,,據稱 已有40棟建築中的住客全部下落不明
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.55,1:43:01.08,up,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.28,1:43:03.79,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.79,1:43:05.64,up,NTP,0,0,0,,成為正義的夥伴…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.83,1:43:06.40,up,NTP,0,0,0,,嗎…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.90,1:43:06.77,up,NTP,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.10,1:43:11.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,希望這一瞬間能永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.45,1:51:23.26,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}請施與我憐惜
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.26,1:51:27.68,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}如同輕撫那墜落的雛鳥
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.68,1:51:30.30,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}請賜予我悲憫
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.30,1:51:32.26,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}願你雙目含淚
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.26,1:51:33.81,cht_lyrics,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100 ,100)}將我俯視
